title: SHOCKER: Tulsi Gabbard Comes Out ...
description:
Tulsi Gabbard surprised the world and has come out … to announce she is no longer a Democrat. We discuss the ramifications. Also, it turns out the liberal Los Angeles City Council is really, really racist. And what’s with PayPay stealing money from customers?
